n류 개발자 (n=3)

Codility - Distinct

02 March 2018

RESULT

import java.util.*;

class Solution {
    public int solution(int[] A) {
        Set<Integer> set = new HashSet<>();
        for (int a : A) {
            set.add(a);
        }
        
        return set.size();
    }
}
